Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:11.30,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:15.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.73,0:00:23.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:27.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:34.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:37.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:45.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:53.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:56.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:04.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:08.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:11.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:15.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:19.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump! Jump, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:42.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In order to save the Rider Kid Corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:46.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the Kamen Rider sacrificed himself\Nto destroy the powerful Centipede Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:51.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He hasn't been seen since.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:56.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is Kamen Rider still out there somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:02:01.72,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx130\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(250.167,160.389)}Evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:02:01.72,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,725.389)}The Fake Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You are needed to test the power\Nof the latest Gel Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, dissolved by my flytrap fluid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My abilities are flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they really, Flytrap Bee?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you beat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown yourself, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on and try me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Flytrap Bee...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If the two of us work together...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,no one on this planet\Ncan hope to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the real Kamen\NRider is still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shocker Rider is ready for action.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very pleased, General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Give orders to the Shocker Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What orders would those be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a group trying to track\Nand stop us since our Shocker days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You must destroy that group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Anti-Shocker Alliance, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll likely try to join hands\Nwith the Rider Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If we send the Shocker Rider at them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll destroy them with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer has a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, put it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:03.16,Italics,,0,0,0,,Urgent situation in process.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:10.02,Italics,,0,0,0,,Anti-Shocker Alliance computer\Nhas discovered our leader's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black, delete that data!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I will deploy the\NShocker Rider at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Any word on Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But let's get looking again.\NWe can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop by HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They might have heard from him by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:09.34,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H365C02&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Kamen Rider \N{\c&H000000&}Kid Corps Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:07:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there, help us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman. Have you heard anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a whole week...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider will return to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Word from Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but it might be related.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to pass information\Nabout Gel Shocker to Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They already hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They just said to come to\NTakeyama Pier by 10:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the time they gave us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Mr. Tachibana Tobei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You have information on Gel Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Our group wants to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Any proof that you aren't with Gel Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're constantly tailing members\Nof the Anti-Shocker Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anti-Shocker Alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll explain the rest later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've brought Mr. Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Anti-Shocker Alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Seiichiro Kogure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker is after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive us for dragging you\Nout to a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Our organization is worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Its members are victims of Gel Shocker\Nfrom all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They killed my only son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They killed my mother, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, allies are always welcome\Nin the battle for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gladly work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our computer has identified\Nthe identity of Gel Shocker's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Their leader's identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:10:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The data will arrive at Shimoda\Nin Izu at 4:00 this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go, Gel Shocker will track us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we were hoping the Kamen\NRider could bring the data to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana. I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Room 406 in Hotel Masaki in Shimoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying there under\Nthe name Ishigami Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to agree,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but we don't know whether\NKamen Rider is dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't tell them that\Nthe Kamen Rider is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had, one of them would go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Gel Shocker would kill that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that the Kamen\NRider is never coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If we want to get to Shimoda\Nby 4:00, we'd better leave soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be all right by\Nyourself, Mr. Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No way out but through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured this would happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to worry you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it best to go into hiding until\Nthe injuries Centipede Tiger gave me healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're all better?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Mr. Taki doesn't have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumekizaki Lighthouse in Izu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I'll accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hear the rest later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a load off my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,467.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,148.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the identity of Gel Shocker's\Nleader really in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our job is just to deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker combatants!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, take care of the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:22.23,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:25.32,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\3c&H536E71&\c&HFFFFFF&}Hotel Masaki
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're late...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They should have been here by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider isn't coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You ridiculous woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great fool you were\Nto pit yourself against Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The very same Kamen\NRider you put your faith in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... you survived, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Gel Shocker\Nsurvives, I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shocker Rider has\Nalready made his move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Shocker Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Help!\N- Who can say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish things with you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the data?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What data?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You traitor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fool me any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider really\Nis working with Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who went to get the\Ndata was my exact double...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shocker Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two Kamen Riders?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying it was the fake\Nwho went to get the data?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I will prove my innocence, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:17:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If he isn't stopped,\Nall our efforts will be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, I will retrieve that data!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I get rid of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the identity of Gel Shocker's leader\Nwill remain a secret forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I just wanted to know their\Nleader's identity as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, you told me not to bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Let's take that\Nto the Anti-Shocker Alliance first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My mission is to destroy\Nthe contents of this tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... have you gone mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly sane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to expose you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But can you, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:39.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:43.25,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:47.27,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:50.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:54.40,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:58.03,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:04.18,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:08.73,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:12.39,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.81,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:26.06,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:30.06,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:33.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:37.44,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:40.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:43.66,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:47.18,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:51.79,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:55.37,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:06.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:09.39,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:13.43,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:16.95,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:20.65,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:23.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:26.95,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:30.33,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:35.11,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:38.38,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:21:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We will erase the ally\Nof justice, Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and let the Shocker Rider take his place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The name Kamen Rider\Nwill forever be cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint, but the name\NKamen Rider will never be disgraced!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's two against one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:01.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Our Kamen Rider faces\Nan unprecedented trial
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:05.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,against Gel Shocker's monstrous\NFlytrap Bee and the Shocker Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:07.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can he make it out alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:10.88,Cont,,0,70,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:13.72,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:13.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In their quest for world domination,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:16.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker has created six Shocker\NRiders identical to the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:19.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their objective is to recover\Nthe data on their leader's identity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:21.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,from the Anti-Shocker Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:24.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The first and second Riders\Nface a battle to the death
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:27.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,against the Shocker Riders\Nin a desolate savanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:31.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.78,0:23:31.21,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(477.167,620.389)}The {\fnOne Stroke Script LET}8 {\fnCienfuegos}Kamen Riders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:39.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The wind gusts across the wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:42.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider traverses it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:46.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Alone, all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:50.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Holding back my sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:54.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I fight, I fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:24:01.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Despite my solitude,\NI will do what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:06.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,to protect my friends and my home
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.57,0:24:12.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I am the Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:56.72,0:02:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil! The Fake Kamen Rider
Comment: 0,0:23:27.78,0:23:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\fnOne Stroke Script LET}8 {\fnCienfuegos}Kamen Riders\NJoin us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider!